(Adapted from Brother
by Qingdeng on Xingjijiaoke)

3
00:00:05,723 --> 00:00:06,460
=Episode 1=

4
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:09,649
(What a harsh world)

5
00:00:09,650 --> 00:00:11,410
(for a downtrodden
illegitimate daughter.)

6
00:00:11,490 --> 00:00:12,739
(After Father's passing,)

7
00:00:12,740 --> 00:00:14,899
(Modesty)
(the General's Mansion falls into decline.)

8
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:18,249
(My brother, the only person in the family
who cared for me, took Father's place)

9
00:00:18,250 --> 00:00:19,859
(to fight on the battlefield.)

10
00:00:19,860 --> 00:00:22,800
(Father's principal wife
trained me to be a suitable concubine)

11
00:00:22,810 --> 00:00:24,920
(for powerful or wealthy men)

12
00:00:25,290 --> 00:00:26,089
(in order to)

13
00:00:26,090 --> 00:00:28,440
(support the entire family.)

14
00:00:31,770 --> 00:00:32,970
Brother.

15
00:00:39,530 --> 00:00:41,290
(Zhen, you're back.)

16
00:00:42,770 --> 00:00:44,480
(Is this a dream?)

17
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:47,800
Chu, I heard

18
00:00:48,940 --> 00:00:50,800
Mother punished you again.

19
00:00:51,490 --> 00:00:52,659
So I came to check on you.

20
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:56,029
♪Won't have to wither♪

21
00:00:56,030 --> 00:00:59,835
♪Obsessive thoughts grow like vines♪

22
00:01:00,118 --> 00:01:03,995
♪Feeding our illusions♪

23
00:01:04,170 --> 00:01:05,320
(Zhen,)

24
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:09,240
(in this lifetime, my heart)

25
00:01:09,940 --> 00:01:11,877
(belongs only to you.)

26
00:01:11,878 --> 00:01:15,884
♪I'll brave the worldly woes♪

27
00:01:15,885 --> 00:01:17,150
(Modesty)

28
00:01:18,450 --> 00:01:21,010
(If only I could be with you)

29
00:01:21,250 --> 00:01:22,600
(forever.)

30
00:01:23,136 --> 00:01:30,628
♪That binds you and me, unwavering♪

31
00:01:34,330 --> 00:01:36,219
You shameless hussy.

32
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:37,779
How dare you

33
00:01:37,780 --> 00:01:38,969
seduce your brother?

34
00:01:38,970 --> 00:01:41,320
Take her to the backyard pond
and drown her.

35
00:01:43,050 --> 00:01:44,160
Zhen.

36
00:01:46,780 --> 00:01:47,960
Chu,

37
00:01:48,610 --> 00:01:50,600
we're blood siblings.

38
00:01:50,610 --> 00:01:53,010
How could you have
such improper thoughts about me?

39
00:02:05,610 --> 00:02:07,219
They're siblings.

40
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:08,209
Does she have no shame?

41
00:02:08,210 --> 00:02:10,040
No wonder
the General's Mansion declined.

42
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:12,739
I can't believe such a disgrace
could happen between siblings.

43
00:02:12,740 --> 00:02:14,259
They've truly shamed
the late General Li.

44
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:16,120
- What a disgraceful act.
- Shameless.

45
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:19,240
(No.)

46
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:21,000
(That's not true.)

47
00:02:21,610 --> 00:02:23,450
(I didn't seduce Zhen.)

48
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:26,240
(I didn't.)

49
00:02:35,450 --> 00:02:37,280
(Why am I dreaming this again?)

50
00:02:39,300 --> 00:02:41,019
(A brother and a sister being together)

51
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:42,680
(is against propriety.)

52
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:44,800
(Zhen has left for a war expedition
for three years.)

53
00:02:44,980 --> 00:02:46,280
(He's returning home today.)

54
00:02:46,650 --> 00:02:48,090
(Li Chuchu,)

55
00:02:48,170 --> 00:02:50,520
(perish that thought.)

56
00:02:53,602 --> 00:02:56,472
(Li's Mansion)

57
00:03:03,050 --> 00:03:04,840
The imperial edict arrives.

58
00:03:04,890 --> 00:03:07,819
Li Zhen of the General's Mansion
defended the nation with great merit.

59
00:03:07,820 --> 00:03:09,889
He will be granted the title
of General Qilin

60
00:03:09,890 --> 00:03:12,120
and be stationed in Anping County.

61
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:23,830
(Glory and Loyalty)

62
00:03:29,890 --> 00:03:31,329
This plaque was endowed by His Majesty

63
00:03:31,330 --> 00:03:32,819
when Old Master was alive.

64
00:03:32,820 --> 00:03:34,649
After his sacrifice,

65
00:03:34,650 --> 00:03:36,369
it was removed.

66
00:03:36,370 --> 00:03:38,520
Finally, it's back now.

67
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,890
From today onwards,

68
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:43,720
no one dares to look down
upon the General's Mansion anymore.

69
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,449
- Congratulations, General Qilin.
- Congratulations, General Qilin.

70
00:03:46,450 --> 00:03:48,880
- Congratulations, Old Madam.
- Congratulations, Old Madam.

71
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:54,960
Mother,

72
00:03:55,020 --> 00:03:56,560
why isn't Chuchu here?

73
00:04:01,890 --> 00:04:03,170
Miss Chuchu,

74
00:04:03,330 --> 00:04:04,680
you have a guest tonight.

75
00:04:10,370 --> 00:04:12,050
She got held up at the moment.

76
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:13,930
You may meet later.

77
00:04:14,100 --> 00:04:16,920
You must be tired from your journey.
Hurry and rest up.

78
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:23,330
Mingyue,

79
00:04:24,130 --> 00:04:25,810
where's Miss Chuchu?

80
00:04:39,100 --> 00:04:42,049
(Now that Zhen has returned gloriously,)

81
00:04:42,050 --> 00:04:43,489
(but I still can't escape)

82
00:04:43,490 --> 00:04:45,600
(this humiliated life.)

83
00:04:45,810 --> 00:04:48,099
(Could death)

84
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:50,280
(be the only way to break free?)

85
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:53,250
(Someone, help me!)

86
00:04:54,490 --> 00:04:56,049
(I was thoughtless.)

87
00:04:56,050 --> 00:04:57,489
(Aside from Mingyue,)

88
00:04:57,490 --> 00:04:59,890
(I should've left Chu
in more trustworthy hands.)

89
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:07,480
Go on.

90
00:05:07,900 --> 00:05:09,360
Run as you like.

91
00:05:09,930 --> 00:05:11,160
I beg of you.

92
00:05:11,740 --> 00:05:13,280
Please spare me.

93
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:25,160
Confound it!

94
00:05:26,010 --> 00:05:28,400
You're spoiled.

95
00:05:36,300 --> 00:05:37,960
(Why must you push me this far?)

96
00:05:38,220 --> 00:05:40,130
(Why do you all have to do this to me?)

97
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:42,960
(All I ever wish for is
a peaceful life.)

98
00:05:43,130 --> 00:05:44,650
