120
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:24,450
I killed someone.

121
00:07:24,740 --> 00:07:25,840
Leave me.

122
00:07:26,900 --> 00:07:27,809
Chu,

123
00:07:27,810 --> 00:07:29,040
listen.

124
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:30,840
I killed the man.

125
00:07:31,460 --> 00:07:34,040
The imperial court has long been furious
with Battalion Commander Liu.

126
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:36,650
The court wouldn't condemn me
for killing him.

127
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:54,770
Chu,

128
00:07:55,930 --> 00:07:57,890
